HEADWORD: Allantoidea
<hw>Al`lan*toid"e*a</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The division of Vertebrata in
